  x Dynamic values are not supported inside at-rule queries (e.g. @media, @container).
  | The query is evaluated by the browser before any CSS variables resolve, so a runtime expression cannot be inserted here.
  | Use a static string or import a constant instead, e.g.:
  | 
  | const desktop = "(min-width: 768px)";
  | styled.div`@media ${desktop} { ... }`
